---

**Test case 1:**

```
    var matches;
    let matches =  null;
    if preg_match("/is([A-Z]\\w+)/", "isLogged()", matches) {
        var_dump(matches);
    }
```

**Output:**

> array(0) { } 

---

**Test case 2:**

```
    var matches;
    let ok =  preg_match("/is([A-Z]\\w+)/", "isLogged()", matches);
    var_dump(matches);
    if ok {
        var_dump(matches);
    }
```

